ASBLENDER
=========================================

ASBlender is an Actionscript 3 library to read and parse Blender .blend files.

The library reads all Blender Objects.
Currently only Mesh objects are linked to the Blender Object.

The mesh is accessible via BlendObject@mesh

Via the mesh you can access vertices, faces and uvt data.

